Package com.frankly.franklysdk.service

Provides interfaces for creating, updating, retrieving, or deleting objects.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Manager.OnChangeListener<T extends StoredObject>
    Called when a StoredObject is created, updated, or deleted.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ConditionalRoomManager
    The main interface for retrieving ConditionalRooms.
    Manager
    The parent class of the interfaces for creating, updating, retrieving, or deleting instances of StoredObject subclasses.
    MessageManager
    The main interface for sending, retrieving, or deleting Messages.
    RoomManager
    The main interface for retrieving or updating Rooms.
    StatisticManager
    The main interface for retrieving Statistics.
    UserManager
    The main interface for retrieving and updating Users.
